---
title: Bacon, Zucchini & Tomato Flatbreads with Lemon Ricotta, Fresh Herbs & Honey
description: If this recipe could talk, it would say “I’m so fancy!” Seriously: You’ve got lemony ricotta cheese that’s fluffy as a cloud, plus bites of tomato and zucchini bursting with juicy goodness, which are all piled onto warm and toasty flatbreads. Oh, and we have to talk about the bling on top: a parsley, chive, and honey garnish that makes each bite light up with herby, spicy, and sweet contrasts. You’ve just hit dinnertime gold.
